Acked-by: Nicolas Ferre <nicolas.ferre@atmel.com>
Acked-by: Eric Bénard <eric@eukrea.com>
Tested-by: Eric Bénard <eric@eukrea.com>
Signed-off-by: Herbert Xu <herbert@gondor.apana.org.au>

